## 2. Design Philosophy

### 2.1 Inspiration Attribution

We draw from multiple sources, each contributing specific elements:

| Source | What We Take | What We DON'T Take |
|--------|--------------|-------------------|
| **Linear App** | Dark mode aesthetic, typography, whitespace, micro-interactions | Sprint/issue tracking patterns (different domain) |
| **JetBrains Fleet Islands UI** | Modular layout, panel separation, information density | IDE-specific features |
| **DHTMLX Gantt** | Timeline visualization, task bars, dependency lines | Light theme default |
| **Railnova Railfleet** | Fleet dashboard patterns, train status indicators | Specific ECM workflows |
| **deck.gl/Kepler.gl** | GPU-accelerated rendering, smooth transitions | Geospatial focus |

### 2.2 Core Principles

1. **Density with Clarity** (Islands UI) - Pack information without overwhelming
2. **Dark Mode First** (Linear) - Reduce eye strain, modern aesthetic
3. **Modular Panels** (Fleet) - Visually separated functional areas
4. **Direct Manipulation** (Gantt) - Drag to reschedule, resize to extend
5. **GPU Performance** (deck.gl) - 60fps even with 15k+ tasks

