**Implementation:** deck.gl HeatmapLayer or GridCellLayer
**Cell Size:** Month × Train row
**Color:** Yellow→Orange→Red gradient based on man-hour density
**Interaction:** Click cell to zoom into that period

### 6.3 MESO View (Tactical - 0.5x to 2.0x)

