## 10. Interactions & Gestures

### 10.1 Canvas Navigation

| Input | Action | Handler |
|-------|--------|---------|
| Drag | Pan canvas | @use-gesture onDrag |
| Scroll wheel | Zoom (cursor-centered) | @use-gesture onWheel |
| Pinch (touch) | Zoom | @use-gesture onPinch |
| Double-click | Zoom in to point | Custom handler |
| Double-tap (touch) | Zoom in to point | Custom handler |

### 10.2 Task Interactions

| Input | Live Mode | Sandbox Mode |
|-------|-----------|--------------|
| Hover | Tooltip | Tooltip + resize handles |
| Click | Select task | Select task |
| Drag task | - | Move (reschedule) |
| Drag edge | - | Resize duration |
| Right-click | View menu | Edit menu |
| Delete key | - | Delete selected |

### 10.3 Keyboard Shortcuts

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `+` / `=` | Zoom in |
| `-` | Zoom out |
| `0` | Reset zoom to 1x |
| Arrow keys | Pan canvas |
| `Escape` | Clear selection |
| `Delete` | Delete task (Sandbox) |
| `Ctrl+Z` | Undo (Sandbox) |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Z` | Redo (Sandbox) |
| `S` | Toggle Sandbox mode |

